        <updateDate>2021-03-29T17:39:07Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Composite Standards Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the National Institute of Standards and Technology to (1) implement the recommendations in a specified report to help facilitate the adoption of composite technology in infrastructure, and (2) conduct a pilot program to assess the feasibility and advisability of adopting such technology in sustainable infrastructure.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
